---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
const seo = {
  title: "About — BrandsBuilders",
  description: "BrandsBuilders builds high-conversion websites, runs ad campaigns, and installs missed-call recovery systems — one flat monthly fee.",
  canonical: "https://brandsbuilders.ca/about"
};
---
<Layout seo={seo}>
<section class="bg-white py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">About BrandsBuilders</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight">
      We build the website, run the ads, and make sure no lead gets lost — one system, one fee.
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
      Most businesses end up juggling a web designer, an ads freelancer, and no real way to track what's working. BrandsBuilders puts all three under one person, one monthly fee, and one report you can actually understand.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-gray-50 py-16 border-y border-gray-200">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Why we exist</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      <p>Most businesses don't have a traffic problem — they have a conversion and follow-up problem. Slow websites, untracked ad spend, and missed calls quietly cost more than any marketing budget.</p>
      <p>We exist to fix all three with one done-for-you system, instead of stitching together three vendors who don't talk to each other.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-white py-16">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Who we work with</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Businesses ready to invest consistently in lead generation — typically $2,000+/month combined between the service fee and ad spend — and ready to move within the next few weeks.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-gray-900 text-white py-16 text-center">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-3xl">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Ready for a system that actually converts?</h2>
    <a href="/apply" class="inline-block mt-4 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 transition">Get Started →</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
